   Use the accumulator pattern with for loop that will find the average of the list below in the code.
   Store the average in a variable called ``my_average``.
   ~~~~
   my_grades = [100, 85, 60, 100, 80, 75, 80, 100] 
   ====
   from unittest.gui import TestCaseGui
   import re
   class myTests(TestCaseGui):
       def testOne(self):
           self.assertEqual(85.0, my_average, 'Checking output.')
	  
   myTests().main()